# AI Self-Review (mandatory before done)

Fix all failures before declaring completion. Log issues in `docs/PROGRESS.md`.

## Checklist

| # | Area | Verify |
|---|------|--------|
| 1 | **Architecture** | 3-zone routes; tre silos; DCAP before LLM; WORM intact |
| 2 | **Performance** | No unnecessary deps; `prefers-reduced-motion`; scale-to-zero |
| 3 | **Accessibility** | Focus visible; aria-labels; 44px touch; contrast on navy/glass |
| 4 | **Design** | Executive Midnight DAD; DS tokens; no new `btn-pill--` in modules |
| 5 | **Tokens** | `--ds-*` / design-system — no hardcoded hex in `src/modules/**` |
| 6 | **Responsive** | 320–1440px; dock clearance; widgets if touched |
| 7 | **Duplication** | Reused existing components (`HubErrorBoundary`, `Button`, etc.) |
| 8 | **Testing** | Relevant smoke + tests for changed behaviour |
| 9 | **Documentation** | `TODO`, `DASHBOARD`, `PROGRESS`, `ROADMAP` (if program), `PROJECT_STATE` (if system) updated |

## UI changes additionally

- `npm run smoke:design-modules`
- `npm run smoke:locked-ux`
- Pontus visual OK per zone (polish, not redesign)

## If any check fails

Fix first. Do not mark TODO complete. Do not skip with "follow-up later" unless Pontus explicitly defers.
